Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior shall appear along with the word of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She shall carry the red lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand amidst golden snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O Savior, please grant us your divine aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:49.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is endless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:56.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My eternal pledge is only for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:03.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wonder if you're your usual self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:08.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll sparkle with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:21.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The arms of the clock advance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:28.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and with them so does time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:35.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}When you are sad, I open my tiny arms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:41.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:50.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is tender
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:56.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I can remember your shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and that wasn't brought about by a program
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:03.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Let us experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:08.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}the turmoil in my heart together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:11.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
