Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.37,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fn@ＤＦＧ勘亭流\blur0.65\b1\fscx93\fs25\c&H4E423E&\move(633,148,633,-20,22,1357)}"We Love Master!" Shinki Haiku Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I'm finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Lene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Both today and tomorrow, \N I really love you.{Leave this \N too}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your writing is unrefined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It really says how you feel about Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we got mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an urgent message from Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I forgot my lunch box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bring it to me before my lunch break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't eat breakfast, so I feel like I'll starve to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Master's going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave now, we can arrive on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,5,,The weather's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,5,,It's perfect for a stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,5,,Stay focused. We are on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm parched...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We played rock-paper-scissors fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should rest here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lene, hit me with a Jellycan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Waaaait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Hey, Lene! {*This is an echo, so make the font smaller.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This hole seems pretty deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, guard the lunch box!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the forgotten city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no place for outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.18,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnLeviBrush\blur1\c&H2B1CC0&\b1\move(452,480,798,706,27,2487)}Bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew something like this was right under the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The place feels... kinda wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell're you? {Her name's AkuAch, Evil Ach. I'll see what I can do about this pun if her name comes up. (It never does.)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah, she's wasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm pretty sure we've been searching for that rice ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this was {\i1}your{\i0} doing? {And this one's WaruYda, Evil Yda. Funny. She still talks in somewhat high-strung language, but now she's totally rude and warui.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll capture you and report you to Empress Claudi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You all better shut your traps if you care about your friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you came here for your master's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who care for their master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,are our allies in this underground empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Underground empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of stray Shinkis who could no longer live with their masters gathered here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and founded this colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't unowned Shinkis supposed to be seized by the manufacturer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We refused that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be reset and lose our memories of our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of Shinkis who felt the same increased one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the city soon grew large.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in poverty, we were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was once a peaceful place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Until {\i1}she{\i0} came. {A different character speaking, so it counts as a different sentence.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,5,,What the heck're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,5,,Empress Claudi, we brought the rice ball criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,5,,Now what were you two thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,5,,bringing somethin' like this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,5,,Well, it wasn't quite a matter of {\i1}thinking{\i0}... {liberal TLs da bes}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,5,,We were taking that to our master,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,5,,and we accidentally dropped it on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What'd you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd you say owns this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... our master's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall never say that word before me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You fuckin' pissed me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, toss 'em in the slavery barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you two ever think you'll see the sun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't those...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kitty, your output's getting pretty fucking weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more power, slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooo! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna curl up with Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(279,221)\an8}I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you've just violated the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(562,0)\an8}I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well at least it makes a good frame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's doggone evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Waaah, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Claudi arrived out of the blue six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She conquered this city by force,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and forbade the very existence of masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinkis of the Anti-Master Army were cast away by their own masters,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and bore dreadful grudges because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All who opposed were made into slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We of the Liberation Army escaped their oppression,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and are now preparing to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With our imprisoned comrades at stake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,failure is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The tailwinds of victory shall soon blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help in any way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our feelings for our masters know no bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who may
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,call me by the name "Hina"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is you, and only you.{Strarf so kyute}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Status report! The patrol unit has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a chance will come at noon today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as the enemy dug up the aged wine we prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Claudi is even bathing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathing in wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to make our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to march at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, you've done well to bear these humiliating days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worked with all your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we will begin our campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Zelnogrard Vanguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you will cause a riot in the slums,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and draw the attention of the enemy army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We will free the slaves within that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, Lene's squad will be deployed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Concurrently, Zil and I will infiltrate the pyramid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack Claudi during her bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeruno, {Her name is in kanji, actually, so I'm going with a more literal reading.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our military force is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it will be difficult, but please hold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I cleaned my guns for this day so much, they're sparkling! {dat heartwarming smile}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take pride, Liberation Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for we shall reclaim peace and freedom once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,O Savior, please save our tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a legend that's spoken of around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When our darkest hour comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,a savior of victory will appear and save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,5,,You two know a lot about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,5,,We have friends here, so we come over to play sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,5,,It was a fun, peaceful place less than a cat year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,5,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Maste—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Waagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That word's forbidden here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a revolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The city's being set aflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zil, I truly thank you for everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want it left unsaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the end, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to seem weak in front of everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oorbel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's win, Zil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the Savior to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has incited mutiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the slums are revolting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess the gutter rats are raising their voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy the soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate with extreme prejudice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, you have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lene!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We should ask {\i1}you{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a crusade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to free the other slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The root of all evil that tramples upon our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring you to justice here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept me waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you think you've been playing hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completely seen you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for someone dumb enough to oppose me to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll have you two kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the greatest show on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like your friends up there to be turned into scrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your cowardice know no bounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you kill each other, or abandon your comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose whichever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding back is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oorbel! Zil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the friends we told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them are really nice Shinkis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were on TV, a hero would show up in the nick of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for stupid fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Strarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were late,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were simply having fun on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}ain't{\i0} fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, unlock the cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Crouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty quick for a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This turned out okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She said Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior shall appear along with the word of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She shall carry the red lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand amidst golden snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! That's just a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How... {\i1}dare{\i0} you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You harmed Master's lunch box!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lene's scary when she gets mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to skedaddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of my love for Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Today marks the birth of a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of work ahead, Zil!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:26.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I stand here reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:31.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and make something of a foolish face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:39.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Being more gentle than the wind and invincible like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:44.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:51.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Here in the forest I am lost in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:57.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to try finding a four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:04.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The sun is guiding me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:10.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}towards the miracles of two stars together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:13.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Even if we are hurt on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:17.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and ten years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:24.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}this future where I can be with you is what I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will walk on ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:30.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not miss the sun's sign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been working to buy Master a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If good little boys and girls hang a stocking by their beds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa will leave a wonderful present inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I first came to Master's house on Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, {\i1}you{\i0} were a Christmas present for Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of being inside Master's stockings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what's on your mind?
